自动选择 = url-test,url=https://www.gstatic.com/generate_204,interval=1800,tolerance=100,timeout=5,select=0,policy-regex-filter=^(?!.*(官网|剩余|流量|套餐|到期|过期|Expire|expire|Traffic|traffic|GB|gb|倍率|重置)).*$
